{"body": "Well, I took a few minutes to make translation opt-in for placeholders using your earlier suggestion. If you still feel it's not a good fit, then go ahead and close the pull. I'd like to use it, and have seen others asking for it. \r\n\r\nThere are other form builders that have better i18n and html5 support, but there's something to be said for the simplicity of the default builder and the builders that sprinkle only limited sugar on top of them. I'd like to see a convention for storing this translation data that both the included form builder and others could leverage.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/2795386", "created_at": "2011-11-18T22:44:59Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/3674#issuecomment-2795386", "updated_at": "2011-11-18T22:44:59Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 3674, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/derekprior/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/derekprior/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/derekprior/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/derekprior", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/derekprior/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/derekprior", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/derekprior/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/79b1b001d5ff186c9bd02e7487aa4142?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F00d021a70eb568ae3a6778add4fed2e9.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/derekprior/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/derekprior/received_events", "gravatar_id": "79b1b001d5ff186c9bd02e7487aa4142", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/derekprior/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "derekprior", "type": "User", "id": 152152, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/derekprior/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "523833b7bd3543c15100fa64"}, "id": 2795386, "issue_url": "https://api.github.